name: Broadway Twisters logo T-Shirt
description:
High quality Fruit of the Loom black T-shirts with Broadway Twisters logo on the front. Please specify at Pal Pal stage if you require size small, medium or large :}

The Broadway Twisters – file under Voodoo-billy/Country-noir.

 Rockabilly trio The Broadway Twisters were formed just a few months ago and performed their stunning live debut at Esquires, Bedford on the 2nd of June 2012 supporting platinum selling artist Paul Young’s new band Los Pacaminos. 

 The Twisters feature slap-bassist Billy J., drummer Sam ‘Wam Bam’ Brunt and vocals/guitar courtesy of Adrian Stranik taking time out from the Silver Brazilians to re-locate his inner Rockabilly. The B.T’s are also proud to present featured vocalist Adele Johnson.
 
Currently performing hi-octane versions of 50’s classics and a few ‘off the beaten track’ toons The Broadway Twisters will be introducing original material into their sets and are expected to evolve into something unique in the coming months. 

Watch this space – don’t touch that dial!

Find The Broadway Twisters on Facebook or contact via broadwaytwisters@hotmail.co.uk
